data.description: Nestled in Mill City on a quiet dead end this 0.23 acre-lot offers more than meets the eye. Boasting 4 beds, 2 baths feat a kitchen oasis complete w/a large island, adorned w/outlets adds a touch of sophistication, complementing the warm laminate flooring that flows seamlessly throughout. TV/Trailer parking that includes a cover, electrical hookups, a large fenced backyard, views of the mountain, a special outlet for a hot tub, & 2 yr old roof, this property harmonizes.
